<P>
   &UR; `STAR WARS' PHENOMENON: THE FORCE TO BE RECKONED WITH &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (NOTE: MAY 29 U.S. opening of `Star Wars' mega-movie) &LR;  &QC;
