   SIDS-CONFERENCE _ ATLANTA _ No one really knows what causes
sudden deaths of seemingly healthy infants, but researchers are
closing in on some clues. The new research will be presented at a
national SIDS conference opening Friday in Atlanta. (Guthrie,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
