<P>
   SHOSHANNA-LINGERIE _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Shoshanna Lonstein,
23, has launched a line of lingerie so insanely popular that stores
can't keep it in stock. There are frocks, too, and soon-to-be
sportswear separates, all for the well-endowed woman. Lonstein, you
may recall from those photo ops with Jerry Seinfeld, is extremely
top heavy. Thing is, she's thin as Wassa Crispbread everywhere
else. Hate her, hate her, hate her. (Grantham, Palm Beach Post)
MOVED.
