<P>
   DEECEE-BEAVER (Washington) _ With stun gun and camera, the Park
Service hunts for a beaver that is chopping down Washington's
famous cherry trees. The ambitious beaver, officials believe, is
seeking to dam the Tidal Basin. However they also believe, perhaps
from dental records, that there is only one beaver involved. By
Michael Janofsky.
