<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-08 16:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0850 &Cx1f; taf-z
s t &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WORLD-ECOTRAVEL-3RDTA     04-08 1317
