<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Friday, April 9, 1999.
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDS: Adds: KOSOVO-AID, KOSOVO-CHEMICAL, CITRUS-CHINA, USDA-BEEF,
VIRUS, DAYTONA, DELL, BUSH-BUCHANAN, TEX-BUSH-TAXCUTS.
