</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TELEMARKETING-BILLING-SPI </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MORE THAN ONE PLAYER INVOLVED IN BILLING 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JANE HADLEY  
 c.1999 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SEATTLE _ Complaints about unauthorized billings to credit cards
are not limited to BrandDirect Marketing.
</P>
<P>
   At least two consumers in Washington state have complained about
a club called SmartSource that is offered by MemberWorks of
Stamford, Conn.
</P>
<P>
   Stephen Lancaster of Wenatchee and Celia Congdon of Vashon
Island say they were billed for membership in SmartSource, a
service that provides discounts and advice on buying electronic
items, yet they were not aware of ever having agreed to it.
</P>
<P>
   Lancaster said in his complaint to the Washington state Attorney
General's Office that he called the number given to him to cancel
``time after time and they always give me the run-around and play
music, then hang up.''
</P>
<P>
   Finally, Lancaster filed the complaint with the Attorney
General's Office, which contacted SmartSource. Lancaster's
membership was then canceled.
</P>
<P>
   When she called SmartSource about the charge on her bill,
Congdon was horrified to discover that she had been billed for the
membership a year ago and had not noticed it. The latest $69.90
membership, a $10 increase over last year's cost, was an automatic
renewal.
</P>
<P>
   SmartSource agreed to remove the latest charge after Congdon's
husband called to protest.
</P>
<P>
   ``I imagine a large percentage just don't call and that's what
they're banking on,'' said Congdon. ``It's really frightening.''
</P>
<P>
   MemberWorks did not respond directly to inquiries from the
Seattle Post-Intelligencer about Congdon's and Lancaster's
complaints, but faxed a ``policy statement'' saying consumers have
the option to cancel the program at any time and to receive a
refund.
</P>
<P>
   Other MemberWorks clubs are Travel Arrangements, Leisure
Advantage, Money Master, and Connections.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
